description:
This is a 28 minute workout called 'The Powerful Release of Letting Go!  Guided Meditation' from the channel Great Meditation.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This is an Original guided meditation recorded by us.    Letting go is not just about releasing attachments to material possessions or past relationships, it's also a spiritual practice that involves surrendering to the flow of life and trusting in a higher power.  It requires us to release our fears, doubts, and worries, and have faith that everything is happening for a divine reason.  Letting go allows us to connect with our true selves and the universe, and to live in a state of peace, love, and harmony.  May we all have the courage to let go of what no longer serves us and trust in the infinite wisdom of the universe.

A special thank you to all our monthly supporters!  
We appreciate all your support and contribution to allow this channel to continue to share our guided meditations with the world.  Thank you!!!
If you would like to join our monthly supporters, you can do so here:  https://www.buymeacoffee.com/greatmeditation/membership
